node.text:
🍣Definitely not regretting our meal🍣 How can anyone simply resist Japanese food?! Our cravings for sashimi and sushi usually comes in weekly💗⁣
⁣
Back to @sushirosingapore for our fatty tuna fix 💗💗 You can now Enjoy their delightful platters with a variety of offerings featuring fatty tuna, salmon, shrimp, grilled eel and more on @grabfoodsg and @foodpandasg delivered right to your doorsteps. Takeaway menu differs so visit their ig for more details 💗⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣⁣

@makanwarrior hahaha foodpanda and grab is just one click away 😂
Oh yesss!!! This all looks so incredibly fresh and yummy. 😍😋
Their fatty Tuna indeed looks very tempting!,
Now I just want some sushi
the marbling of that tina is insane 😱
@fitfoodie_tas hahhaa I haven had it for quite a while too
I love sushi!!! It's been so long since I've had it. I would devour this
OMG that fatty tuna!!😍😍 Missing sushi SOOO much!!
Looove that eel and fatty tuna!! 🔥
@wishuponatart same to you!!!!! Enjoy time with your precious 💗
